profile_positions.description:
‘Summairu’, a Tamil word used by an enlightened Master from the East, Ramana Marharshi, means ‘just be’ or ‘just being’. We discover that when one is not trying to be this or that, but just simply being in silence without mind, it leads to pure awareness. When this pure awareness acts, it is a love in action — it includes and transforms humanity and other life on earth.

Here at Summairu, we integrate and offer business consulting with in-house general counsel as a service with the same awareness and make it our mission: empowering business visionaries to be future-fit consciously and legally. It is a way of life and the pivot on which modern businesses thrive: one that enriches humanity and other life on earth.

Our services include:
>>> International business advisory
>>> Contract services
>>> Intellectual property
>>> Company incorporation
>>> GDPR & data protection
>>> Cross-border transactions

Key responsibilities and achievements:

• Assisting a Japan public company listed on NASDAQ and Japan Stock Exchange for data protection officer services in The Netherlands. 

• Handling cross-border transactions such as: 

>> Series A funding investment of USD1 million for a digital marketing agency in Thailand and monitoring and closing of the transaction; and
>>	Sale and purchase agreements of residential properties with a total valued of RM2.3 million for a Malaysian client.

• Acting as a general counsel for: 

>> an F&B client in the UAE in the drafting and reviewing its franchise and licensing agreements worldwide.
>> a multi-awarded tech scaleup in the UAE which has worldwide presence for its day to day contracts and overseeing its incorporation in The Netherlands as well as drafting and/or reviewing of incorporation documents and the shareholders’ agreement. 
>> an e-commerce company setting up its presence in The Netherlands and in drafting its contracts.  
>> a Dubai education group with growing presence for its day to day contracts.

A centre of learning offering meditations and programs created by Dhyan Vimal, a well-known enlightened teacher and scholar within the field of human transformation. Dhyan Vimal's teachings are made available through DV Institute for Higher Learning Inc. and are licensed to and organised by Dhyan Vimal Centres around the world.

We are honoured to share the work as a part of Dhyan Vimal and Friends to Mankind's Global Peace Effort to bring awareness to the inherent right of each human being to live as someone who can shape life. The meditation sessions and workshops are suitable for individuals and organisations who seek growth, leadership awareness, EQ and breakthrough performance. These are being offered both online or in-person in Rotterdam and within Europe.

Key responsibilities:

• Overseeing the daily operations and facilitating mediation sessions and leadership workshops.
